  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A Global Friendship creates economic opportunity for artisans in developing regions by building market access and small business skills. Proceeds from sales go back to the artisans and their communities. In addition to opportunity, A Global Friendship provides community development projects in accordance to the need of our artisan&apos;s communities. Our focus in Peru will be to build sinks and toilets in the community&apos;s primary school, and a dental check up for the children with a volunteer dentist.</narrative>
